--
-- Generated ONCE by api/scripts/gen-route-legs.mjs against a locally-run
-- OpenRouteService (Docker, OSM Malaysia extract) — there is no runtime routing
-- provider, no API key and no quota. See the RouteLeg model in schema.prisma for
-- why a finite table can cover every route the system can ask for, and for the
-- condition under which that stops being true (geocoded consignee addresses).
--
-- The INSERTs below are appended by the generator script; do not hand-edit them.
-- To refresh: re-run the script and ship a NEW migration rather than editing
-- this one (applied migrations must never change).

